more than their hands.

35:47.187 --> 35:51.567
About 10,000 years ago
our ancestors all over the world...

35:51.733 --> 35:55.237
...took advantage of another form
of climate change...

35:55.403 --> 35:59.453
...the gentler climate of the intermission
in the Ice Age.

35:59.616 --> 36:03.086
They invented agriculture.

36:03.244 --> 36:06.794
They gave up the ceaseless wandering,
hunting and gathering...

36:06.956 --> 36:10.426
